<h1>Login</h1>
<p>Please login to access the site.</p>
<form action="/user/login" method="post">
    <div style="text-align: left;">
        <label for="email">Email:</label>
        <br>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: left;">
        <label for="password">Password:</label>
        <br>
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
    </div>
    <button type="submit">Login</button>
</form>

<p style="margin-top: 50px">Don't have an account? <a href="/user/register">Register here!</a></p>

<p style="margin-top: 300px;">By logging in, you agree that we will store and process your data to provide you with our services. We respect your privacy and will handle your data in accordance with our Privacy Policy.</p>